//&nbsp;allows&nbsp;the&nbsp;user&nbsp;to&nbsp;add&nbsp;procedurally&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;filters&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;command&nbsp;line<br>
